file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: userapi
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
- description: development
  url: http://localhost:8080
paths:
  /users:
    get:
      description: Userをすべて取得する
      operationId: getUsers
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Users'
          description: Userの配列
components:
  responses:
    Users:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Users'
      description: Userの配列
  schemas:
    Users:
      example:
        users:
        - name: po3rin
          id: 1
        - name: po3rin
          id: 1
      properties:
        users:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/UserProperties'
          type: array
      required:
      - users
      type: object
    UserProperties:
      example:
        name: po3rin
        id: 1
      properties:
        id:
          example: 1
          format: int32
          type: integer
        name:
          example: po3rin
          type: string
      required:
      - id
      - name
      type: object
